snippet.title: Danganronpa V3: Killing Harmony - Announcement Trailer (PS4, PS Vita)
snippet.description:
Learn more @ http://danganronpa.us/v3

Welcome to a new world of Danganronpa, and prepare yourself for the biggest, most exhilarating episode yet. Meet cool new characters, investigate twisted murder scenes, and condemn your new friends to death.

Check out the limited edition at http://store.nisamerica.com/games/danganronpa-v3-killing-harmony-limited-edition-ps4
